cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.HC 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to recommend stickers in a messaging app. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves clustering and prediction models, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses the efficacy of different approaches to train embeddings, which could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper also considers the limitations of low-end phones, which could be relevant to cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction).
